呢？ ——— 问题中不应该是意大利人的苦难而应该是美国底层人的苦难抱歉… 非常抱歉提问的时候没想太清楚，我不打算修改问题不然后来者会觉得莫名奇妙的。"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ir6DX69fBzwIQAxoINzA3MzgxNTcgus+jigYwKji8C0ABcgk0ODgwNTQwMTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"2316 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-24bb95c23c5a4e90b4b65ebfb1087fb2_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1632643711.6350367","card_id":"Q_488750262","target":{"id":488750262,"title":"如何看待美国竟敢在这时候宣布打开国门，全球防疫迎重大转折？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/488750262","type":"question","created":1632471293,"answer_count":543,"follower_count":2516,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[307,4080,575162,575501,583976],"comment_count":127,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"一个久违的好消息？或者，未来将更糟的消息！ 现在是该高兴还是担忧，谁也说不准。 近日，白宫表示计划从 11 月初开始对打完疫苗的旅客放宽入境限制，只要接种完疫苗，并且持有 72 小时核酸阴性证明即可。"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ir6DX69fBzwIQAxoINzA4OTI4NTIg/ZG2igYwfzjUE0ACcgk0ODg3NTAyNjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"1183 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-0b5521f6db0e3e98ed8b8cebcc08c918_720w.jpeg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1632643711.635599","card_id":"Q_488626868","target":{"id":488626868,"title":"《鱿鱼游戏》中的老头如何保证自己不会死在游戏中？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/488626868","type":"question","created":1632422212,"answer_count":125,"follower_count":449,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4118,44844,213156,568484,713447],"comment_count":8,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"像夜晚大乱斗的不确定性，拔河如果不是男二也应该要下去了，所以老头是真的来体验还是有死的觉悟玩的？"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ir6DX69fBzwIQAxoINzA4NjUzNTggxJKzigYwCDjBA0ADcgk0ODg2MjY4Njh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","det